dc_title_s: Replication data for: Census PUMFs Variable Guide
dc_description_s: This spreadsheet contains Census Canada Individual PUMFs variable labels and definitions from 1971 to 2006. The file was compiled using “Variables from Individual PUMFs, 1971-1996” spreadsheet prepared by Walter Giesbrecht of York University.
dc_creator_sm: Walter Giestbrecht, Alia Ahmad,  Elaine Grisola, Joshua Mildenberger and Nazia Sheikh
